{"tid":2442393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【表忠一覽】保安局及 6 紀律部隊極速表態擁護人大決定","createTime":"2021-03-11T10:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T10:39:13.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38e510bb843f3f42abd0bedac543898f444e16df","tid":2442393,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:19:39.000Z","msg":"【表忠一覽】保安局及 6 紀律部隊極速表態擁護人大決定<br />\n<br />\n全國人大下午閉幕，特區政府各司局隨即分別發表共 14 篇聲明，支持人大「完善」香港選舉制度或「十四五」規劃綱要。保安局及其管轄的 6 個主要紀律部隊更於半小時內，相繼發稿共 7 篇，表明「全力支持」人大「完善」選舉制度；當中包括警務處處長、海關關長、入境事務處處長、懲教署署長、消防處處長及飛行服務隊均表示全力支持全國人大落實「愛國者治港」，內容大同小異。"},{"pid":"9d0c5ad2dd7627a4f0822cb5391ad067bd26b2c3","tid":2442393,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"From TG"},{"pid":"aee714964cbe68b099ef36ba8d9197fa78e54c8e","tid":2442393,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"吾皇萬歲萬歲萬萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef45a0c6ce3238d092e57a2133726016243a078","tid":2442393,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"新任既愛國廣播處長呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪又係縱容黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd9ea978b9992cb4a934dcade784e6b293fcf4b","tid":2442393,"uid":276273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"科興都唔打，去打BioNTech，<br />\n示咗忠啦，但忠既一定唔係......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e2de04ca7fdc354066fca733a7042df3541552","tid":2442393,"uid":265318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"「威&middot;毽&middot;面&middot;虎&middot;貓！」"}